msgid "Running the coordinator"
msgstr "运行协调器"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:12
msgid "The coordinator is a FastAPI service. Start it with:"
msgstr "协调器是一个 FastAPI 服务。使用以下命令启动它："

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:18
