msgid "``--coordinator-advertise-ip``"
msgstr "``--coordinator-advertise-ip``"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:90
msgid "``LMCACHE_COORDINATOR_ADVERTISE_IP``"
msgstr "``LMCACHE_COORDINATOR_ADVERTISE_IP``"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:91
msgid ""
"IP the coordinator should reach this server at (defaults to the server's "
"outbound IP)."
msgstr "协调器应通过此服务器访问的 IP（默认为服务器的外部 IP）。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:93
msgid "``--coordinator-heartbeat-interval``"
msgstr "``--coordinator-heartbeat-interval``"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:94
msgid "``LMCACHE_COORDINATOR_HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL``"
msgstr "``LMCACHE_COORDINATOR_HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL``"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:95
msgid ""
"Seconds between heartbeats (must be ``> 0``, default ``5``). Keep it well"
" below the coordinator's ``INSTANCE_TIMEOUT``."
msgstr "心跳之间的秒数（必须为 ``> 0``，默认值为 ``5``）。保持远低于协调器的 ``INSTANCE_TIMEOUT``。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:97
msgid "``--coordinator-l2-event-reporting``"
msgstr "``--coordinator-l2-event-reporting``"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:98
msgid "``LMCACHE_COORDINATOR_L2_EVENT_REPORTING``"
msgstr "``LMCACHE_COORDINATOR_L2_EVENT_REPORTING``"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:99
msgid ""
"Enable reporting L2 store/lookup events to the coordinator for fleet-wide"
" usage tracking and quota-based eviction."
msgstr "启用向协调器报告 L2 存储/查找事件，以便进行全队列使用跟踪和基于配额的逐出。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:101
msgid "``--coordinator-l2-event-flush-interval``"
msgstr "``--coordinator-l2-event-flush-interval``"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:102
msgid "``LMCACHE_COORDINATOR_L2_EVENT_FLUSH_INTERVAL``"
msgstr "``LMCACHE_COORDINATOR_L2_EVENT_FLUSH_INTERVAL``"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:103
msgid "Seconds between L2 event batch flushes (must be ``> 0``, default ``1``)."
msgstr "L2 事件批量刷新之间的秒数（必须为 ``> 0``，默认值为 ``1``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:105
msgid ""
"The server registers under its telemetry identity (``--service-instance-"
"id`` / OTel ``service.instance.id``); if that is unset, the coordinator "
"assigns an id."
msgstr ""
"服务器在其遥测身份下注册 (``--service-instance-id`` / OTel "
"``service.instance.id``)；如果未设置，则协调器会分配一个 ID。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:108
msgid ""
"Registration is best-effort: if the coordinator is unreachable, the MP "
"server logs a warning, keeps retrying, and continues serving. A malformed"
" heartbeat-interval value is rejected at startup."
msgstr "注册是尽力而为的：如果协调器无法访问，MP 服务器会记录警告，持续重试，并继续提供服务。启动时会拒绝格式错误的心跳间隔值。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:113
msgid "Inspecting the fleet"
msgstr "检查集群"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:115
msgid "Two read-only endpoints let you observe the coordinator:"
msgstr "两个只读端点让您观察协调器："

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:117
msgid "``GET /instances`` -- list every registered MP server."
msgstr "``GET /instances`` -- 列出每个注册的 MP 服务器。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:118
msgid "``GET /healthz`` -- coordinator liveness probe (for Kubernetes)."
msgstr "``GET /healthz`` -- 协调器存活探测（用于 Kubernetes）。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:129
msgid "L2 usage tracking and eviction"
msgstr "L2 使用跟踪和逐出"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:131
msgid ""
"When MP servers enable ``--coordinator-l2-event-reporting``, they stream "
"L2 store and lookup events to the coordinator. The coordinator aggregates"
" per-``cache_salt`` usage, enforces quotas, and selects LRU keys to "
"evict."
msgstr "当 MP 服务器启用 ``--coordinator-l2-event-reporting`` 时，它们将 L2 存储和查找事件流式传输到协调器。协调器聚合每个 ``cache_salt`` 的使用情况，强制执行配额，并选择 LRU 键进行逐出。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:135
msgid ""
"Each event batch carries the server's ``instance_id`` and a monotonically"
" increasing sequence number (``seq``) scoped to that instance. These "
"fields enable future gap detection to identify lost batches."
msgstr "每个事件批次携带服务器的 ``instance_id`` 和一个单调递增的序列号 (``seq``)，该序列号限定于该实例。这些字段使未来的缺口检测成为可能，以识别丢失的批次。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:139
msgid ""
"**Quota management** -- set per-``cache_salt`` byte budgets. Salts "
"without a quota default to a 0-byte limit (allowlist semantics)."
msgstr "**配额管理** -- 为每个 ``cache_salt`` 设置字节预算。没有配额的盐默认为 0 字节限制（白名单语义）。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:154
msgid "Use ``_default`` as the path parameter to target the empty-string salt."
msgstr "使用 ``_default`` 作为路径参数以定位空字符串盐。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:156
msgid ""
"**Event ingestion** -- MP servers POST batched events; this is handled "
"automatically by the event listener and is not typically called manually."
msgstr "**事件摄取** -- MP 服务器通过 POST 批量事件；这由事件监听器自动处理，通常不需要手动调用。"

#: ../../source/mp/coordinator.rst:172
msgid "**Status queries** -- inspect usage and quota info."
msgstr "**状态查询** -- 检查使用情况和配额信息。"

